These handle data processing, business logic, authentication, and database communication.
Programming Languages
•	JavaScript (Node.js)
•	Python (Django, Flask)
•	Java (Spring, Spring Boot)
•	PHP (Laravel)
•	C# (.NET)
Back-End Frameworks
•	Express.js (Node.js)
•	Django / Flask (Python)
•	Spring Boot (Java)
•	Laravel (PHP)
